23:06.552 --> 23:10.305
♪ We'll ride them someday ♪

23:10.389 --> 23:14.143
[girl on TV] Sorry we didn't
get you a birthday present.

23:14.226 --> 23:16.228
I got so distracted by
trying to get tickets

23:16.311 --> 23:18.272
to the New Kids On The Block concert,

23:18.355 --> 23:20.983
I completely lost sight
of what's important.

23:21.067 --> 23:23.986
And I got so swept up in my
campaign for class president,

23:24.070 --> 23:26.906
I forgot why I was
running in the first place.

23:26.989 --> 23:28.908
And I was boy crazy.

23:28.991 --> 23:31.035
Kids, kids, I don't need a present.

23:31.119 --> 23:33.245
I got everything I need right here.

23:33.328 --> 23:34.413
[audience] Aww.

23:34.496 --> 23:37.458
