- Sabrina.

23:37.541 --> 23:39.668
Come here, you goofball.

23:39.752 --> 23:40.753
[applause]

23:40.836 --> 23:44.840
[closing theme music]

23:47.217 --> 23:50.054
[overlapping chatter]

23:50.179 --> 23:52.890
[laughter]

23:52.974 --> 23:55.851
- Aha.
- Whoa.

23:55.935 --> 23:57.603
- Can you make it out to Blake?
- Uh-huh.

23:57.686 --> 24:00.106
Thanks, man. You're, like, my hero.

24:00.189 --> 24:02.399
Really?

24:02.483 --> 24:03.484
Huh.

